38
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:11,230
Co je, mizero?

39
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:18,490
Co to je?
Viděla to Dok Mi?

40
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:21,960
Je někdo doma? O co jde?

41
